summary: An ordinance providing for the rezoning of Lots 21 to 24, Block 5, Salmon Bay 2nd Addition, located on the northeast corner of 6th Avenue Northwest and West 79th Street; and Lots 17 to 29 inclusive, Block 9, Ravenna Springs Park Supplemental Addition; Blocks 1 and 2, Dorffel's Supplemental to Wassom's Addition; and the unplatted land adjoining, located on 25th Avenue Northeast between Blakely Street and East 54th Street.
